column4: BriefDescription
Counts any Prefetch requests that are outstanding, per weighted cycle, from the time of the request to when any response is received. The oustanding response should be programmed only on PMC0.
Counts any Prefetch requests that accounts for responses from a snoop request hit with data forwarded from its Far(not in the same quadrant as the request)-other tile's L2 in M state.
